Taskwarrior scripts
===================

Description
-----------

Scripts and hooks for Taskwarrior:

 - rmattr: deletes tags or properties from a task when modified


Installation
------------

rmattr

1. Copy `rmattr` and `rmattr.ini` to Taskwarrior "hooks" directory
   (`~/.task/hooks` by default)
3. Create a link:  `ln -s rmattr on-modify-rmattr`
2. Edit `rmattr.ini` and set desired values

For more information consult Taskwarrior documentation over at
https://taskwarrior.org/docs/


